data.description: Welcome to your picture-perfect dream home in the heart of San Juan! This delightful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is brimming with charm and offers a refreshing open-concept layout that is as inviting as it is functional. Recently updated, this home blends modern elegance with cozy comforts, offering you the perfect balance between contemporary living and timeless appeal. The kitchen is a true gem, with sleek countertops, and ample storage space. Cooking and entertaining will be a pleasure. This adorable and well-maintained home won't stay on the market for long! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours.
